-----------------| How to Install? |------------------
------------------------------------------------------

1. Put the &#039;XBOXLogo&#039; folder in the &#039;data&#039; folder of 
   your M.U.G.E.N. Directory.

2. Open the &#039;system.def&#039; file of the &#039;data&#039; folder.
   Go to &#039;[Files]&#039; section and replace the line:
   &#039;logo.storyboard = &#039; with:
   &#039;logo.storyboard = XBOXLogo/XBOXLogo.def&#039;
   and save it.
